{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<semantics>","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>MathML においては、数学をタグ付けるには二つの方法があり、<em>表示 (presentation)</em> MathML が数式の配置を制御するのに用いられる一方、<em>内容 (content)</em> MathML は数式の論理的意味の符号化及び数式処理系 (computer algebra system) に適するような数式の変換を念頭に設計されています。MathML 要素<code>&lt;semantics&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;annotation&gt;</code>及び<code>&lt;annotation-xml&gt;</code>を用いることで、表示 MathML と内容 MathML を組み合せ、数式の配置情報及び論理的意味の双方を記述できます。</p>\n<p><code>&lt;semantics&gt;</code>要素は注釈に関連したコンテナ要素として振舞い、子要素を持たなくてはなりません（そうでない場合、<em>無効なタグ付け</em>として誤り報告されます）。<code>&lt;annotation&gt;</code>要素には非 XML 形式の論理的情報が含まれ、対して<code>&lt;annotaiton-xml&gt;</code>要素には XML 形式の情報（例: 内容 MathML や OpenMath）が含まれます。</p>\n<p><code>&lt;semantics&gt;</code>要素における可視子要素を決定する規則を次に挙げます。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>適用すべき規則がない場合: 既定では最初の子要素のみ描画しますが、当要素は表示 MathML でなくてはなりません。</li>\n  <li>最初の子要素が<code>&lt;annotation&gt;</code>又は<code>&lt;annotation-xml&gt;</code>以外の表示 MathML 要素の場合、当要素が描画されます。</li>\n  <li>\n    表示 MathML が見当らない場合、<code>&lt;semantics&gt;</code>要素の最初の<code>&lt;annotation&gt;</code>又は<code>&lt;annotation-xml&gt;</code>子要素を描画します。\n    <code>encoding</code>属性で次の孰れかが指定されている場合、<code>&lt;annotation-xml&gt;</code>要素のみが認識されることに気を付けてください。\n    <ul>\n      <li>application/mathml-presentation+xml</li>\n      <li>MathML-Presentation</li>\n      <li>SVG1.1</li>\n      <li>text/html</li>\n      <li>image/svg+xml</li>\n      <li>application/xml</li>\n    </ul>ここに「application/mathml+xml」を挙げて<em>いない</em>ことに留意してください、というのもこれでは内容 MathML か表示 MathML かを区別できないからです。\n  </li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>&lt;annotation&gt;</code>及び<code>&lt;annotation-xml&gt;</code>要素には次の属性が設定できます。</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"definitionurl\">definitionURL</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The location of the annotation key symbol.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"encoding\">encoding</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>当注釈における論理的情報の符号化方法（例: 「MathML-Content」、「MathML-Presentation」、「application/openmath+xml」、「image/png」）。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cd\">cd</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The content dictionary that contains the annotation key symbol.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"name\">name</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The name of the annotation key symbol.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"src\">src</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>論理的情報の為の外部資源の場所。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>semantics</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 表示MathML --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>x<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>+<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>y<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 内容MathML --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>annotation-xml</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">encoding</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>MathML-Content<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>apply</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>plus</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>apply</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>power</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ci</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>x<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ci</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>cn</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>integer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>cn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>apply</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ci</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>y<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ci</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>apply</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>annotation-xml</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 画像注釈 --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>annotation</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">encoding</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>image/png<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>some/path/formula.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- TeX形式の注釈 --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>annotation</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">encoding</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>application/x-tex<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      x^{2} + y\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>annotation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>semantics</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>仕様</th>\n      <th>状態</th>\n      <th>備考</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter5.html\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 3.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">Mixing Markup Languages for Mathematical Expressions の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n      <td>現在の仕様</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML2/chapter5.html\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 2.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">Combining Presentation and Content Markup  の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n      <td>初期の仕様</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザー互換機","id":"ブラウザー互換機","isH3":false,"query":"mathml.elements.semantics","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_固有の注記","title":"Gecko 固有の注記","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>(Firefox 23 / Thunderbird 23 / SeaMonkey 2.20)において、semantics 要素下の可視子要素を決定する算法が MathML 仕様に準じるよう修正されました。以前では、最初の子要素が〔無条件に〕描画されていました。</li>\n  <li>Gecko では、src 属性が指定されている場合、<code>&lt;annotation&gt;</code>及び<code>&lt;annotation-xml&gt;</code>は無視されます。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様","id":"仕様"},{"text":"ブラウザー互換機","id":"ブラウザー互換機"},{"text":"Gecko 固有の注記","id":"gecko_固有の注記"}],"summary":"MathML においては、数学をタグ付けるには二つの方法があり、表示 (presentation) MathML が数式の配置を制御するのに用いられる一方、内容 (content) MathML は数式の論理的意味の符号化及び数式処理系 (computer algebra system) に適するような数式の変換を念頭に設計されています。MathML 要素<semantics>、<annotation>及び<annotation-xml>を用いることで、表示 MathML と内容 MathML を組み合せ、数式の配置情報及び論理的意味の双方を記述できます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<semantics>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/mathml/element/semantics","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/mathml/element/semantics/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element","title":"MathML 要素リファレンス"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics","title":"<semantics>"}],"pageTitle":"<semantics> - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}